1.00	True_Democracy_(album)	True Democracy (album)	True Democracy is a roots reggae album released by Steel Pulse in May 1982. The album was recorded over 25 days in Denmark, with legendary reggae producer Karl Pitterson.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/5/5e/Steelpulse_truedemocracy.jpg/220px-Steelpulse_truedemocracy.jpg
